<TEXT>
Observer would like to thank respondents to last week's 'Musing' teaser for
their ingenious replies. The bottle of finest malt goes to William Pitt, the
first reader correctly to identify the reference concerning advances French
insurer Assurances Generales de France is making on the reluctant maiden,
